{"tid":2039452,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港股今早低開後急升 經數輪升趺後繼無力 中午跌422點","createTime":"2020-05-28T04:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T08:11:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"7798e10f2c13616a49ff9d818b0879c8a35dc0ab","tid":2039452,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"港股中午跌422點 石藥急跌12%<br />\n28.05.2020 12:16<br />\n<br />\n人大政協今日將表決港區國安法，美國指考慮對香港採取行動，港股在期指結算日下跌，恒生指數低開94點，初段曾調頭回升，其後持續向下，恒指跌至半日低位，中午收報22878點，跌422點，跌幅1.8%，成交額686億元。國企指數報9464點，跌102點，跌幅1%。<br />\n<br />\n藍籌股普遍下跌，騰訊(<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=c07ff57e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>)跌3%，報406.4元，拖低恒指90點，港交所(<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=7e4b31c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)亦跌3%，報264.6元，匯控(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=d189a304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>)跌逾1%，報36.75元。醫藥股受壓，石藥集團(<a href=\"http://01093.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01093.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=62ae20b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01093.HK</a>)業績後回吐12%，報14.9元，跌2.04元，是半日跌幅最大藍籌，中國生物製藥(<a href=\"http://01177.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01177.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=82cc563e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01177.HK</a>)跌逾6%，報11.14元，跌0.8元。<br />\n<br />\n本地地產股繼續下跌，新世界發展(<a href=\"http://00017.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00017.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=7cc8eb5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00017.HK</a>)跌4%，報7.76元，領展(<a href=\"http://00823.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00823.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=8ece8059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00823.HK</a>)跌近4%，報56.5元。恒地(<a href=\"http://00012.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00012.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=6946e127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00012.HK</a>)跌3%，報27.5元。另外，申洲國際(<a href=\"http://02313.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02313.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=466381d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02313.HK</a>)逆市升近2%，報90.85元，升1.75元，是半日升幅最大藍籌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292336&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1292336%26csid%3D261_368&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=6806d3f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292336&amp;csid=261_368</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44u7F45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44u7F45.png&h=cd75e38b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f2cc9491f86630d66bc777295d00c8500d83ff2","tid":2039452,"uid":68689,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"全國人大第三次全體會議閉幕於下午3時舉行<br />\nLM睇3點後個市"},{"pid":"cc463a2cd403f1487b6ef0ff24181ac13f323403","tid":2039452,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"托水龍"},{"pid":"63e5c964684191b66239a7d0e210a9df2e1a02ac","tid":2039452,"uid":196924,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"支狗托唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c6cdaf1aaa55603037bc08d839123aab39d349","tid":2039452,"uid":300006,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0