DM0839cs%3D&h=7e4b31c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)亦跌3%，報264.6元，匯控(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=d189a304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>)跌逾1%，報36.75元。醫藥股受壓，石藥集團(<a href=\"http://01093.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01093.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=62ae20b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01093.HK</a>)業績後回吐12%，報14.9元，跌2.04元，是半日跌幅最大藍籌，中國生物製藥(<a href=\"http://01177.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01177.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=82cc563e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01177.HK</a>)跌逾6%，報11.14元，跌0.8元。<br />\n<br />\n本地地產股繼續下跌，新世界發展(<a href=\"http://00017.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00017.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=7cc8eb5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00017.HK</a>)跌4%，報7.76元，領展(<a href=\"http://00823.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00823.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=8ece8059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00823.HK</a>)跌近4%，報56.5元。恒地(<a href=\"http://00012.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00012.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=6946e127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00012.HK</a>)跌3%，報27.5元。另外，申洲國際(<a href=\"http://02313.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02313.HK&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=466381d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02313.HK</a>)逆市升近2%，報90.85元，升1.75元，是半日升幅最大藍籌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292336&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1292336%26csid%3D261_368&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=6806d3f7\